data.description:
MOTIVATED SELLER!Welcome to the epitome of desert living in Florence Gardens a 55+ community in Florence, Arizona! This exceptional 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom double wide manufactured home and adjacent lot offers not only a comfortable and modern interior but also breathtaking views that encapsulate the essence of Arizona's beauty.
Nestled within the highly sought-after Florence Gardens community, this home presents an inviting blend of spaciousness and style. As you step inside, you're greeted by a semi open-concept layout that seamlessly integrates the living, dining, and kitchen areas. However, the true allure of this property lies outdoors. Step onto the expansive patio, where the vistas of the surrounding beauty are on full display.
